
# VitalCheck - AI-Powered Symptom Checker

## 📌 Project Overview
**VitalCheck** is an AI-powered medical assistant that analyzes user symptoms and provides possible disease predictions using **Google Gemini AI**. This project aims to leverage AI in healthcare to enhance early diagnosis and medical accessibility.

## 🚀 Features
- ✅ **AI-Driven Predictions** – Uses **Google Gemini AI** for fast and accurate symptom analysis.
- ✅ **Interactive UI** – Built with **Streamlit** for an intuitive user experience.
- ✅ **Privacy-Focused** – No user data is stored.
- ✅ **Multi-Symptom Input** – Users can enter multiple symptoms at once.
- ✅ **Easy to Use** – Simple interface with real-time analysis.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Google Gemini AI** – For advanced symptom analysis.
- **Streamlit** – To create an interactive UI.
- **Python** – For backend logic and API integration.
- **Lottie Animations** – To enhance user experience.

## 📂 Project Structure
```
VitalCheck/
│── app.py  # Main application file
│── ui_ux.py  # UI styling and animations
│── requirements.txt  # Project dependencies
│── README.md  # Project documentation
```

## 🔧 Installation & Setup
### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/VitalCheck.git
cd VitalCheck
```

### 2️⃣ Install Dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3️⃣ Run the Application
```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

## 🏥 How It Works
1. Users select or enter symptoms.
2. The AI model analyzes the symptoms using **Google Gemini AI**.
3. The app provides **potential conditions** with explanations.
4. Users can refine their symptoms for better accuracy.

## 📌 Future Improvements
- 🔹 **Expand symptom database** for better accuracy.
- 🔹 **Multilingual support** for wider accessibility.
- 🔹 **Integrate medical knowledge databases** for additional insights.

## 📜 Disclaimer
VitalCheck is an AI-powered **symptom checker**, not a replacement for professional medical advice. Always consult a healthcare provider for diagnosis and treatment.

